metadata.name: Collab Zine # 1 - Hallow-zine
metadata.description:
A collaborative NFT Zine with some of the coolest (and spookiest folks in Web3.

Follow the steps to access your files:  
1. Go to our token gated site https://tell.ie/u/Collabzine  
2. Find the Hallowzine Token Gate Button  
3. Log in with the wallet that holds the token  
4. You will be taken to a page to download the jpegs, .PDF files of the zine, and read the zine on your phone.

60 pages of jam packed art and spook-tility:

Vansh embraces the art of a horror lover, and spooky squiggles.

Ntxoo unearths the spookiest creatures in pots.. sort of.

Aly shares why she hated being a witch for Halloween.

Jack tells some jokes, makes puzzles, and creates the cutest lil' fragile friends.

Lisa makes  paper dolls that have legendary and out of this world outfits.

Eislyn shares what she gives out for Halloween instead of candy.

Riley transmutes the beautiful, whimsical and the absurd into poetry.

But don't just take our word for it!
